dct_description_sm: Bergen County, New Jersey map compiled from state official records and maps and recent private surveys. Map indicates the following road types: Macadam or good roads, fair roads, all others and street car lines. Map includes advertisement from North Jersey Title Insurance Co., Hackensack, N.J.
